import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Users } from '../users'; import { UserServiceService } from '../user-service.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-userlist', templateUrl: './userlist.component.html', styleUrls: ['./userlist.component.css'] }) export class UserlistComponent { users: Users[]; constructor(private userService: UserServiceService) { this.users = []; } ngOnInit() { this.userService.getUsers().subscribe((data: Users[]) => { this.users = data; }); } }
